  /etc/rc.d/init.d directory.

  28 Apr 2002; Arcady Genkin <agenkin@thpoon.com>
	alsa-driver-0.9.0_rc1-r3.ebuild :

  More work on the startup script and updated config file for /etc/modules.d.
